main_body:
Annex I to Regulation (EC) No 2505/96 is hereby amended as follows:
1. the tariff quotas for the products listed in Annex I to this Regulation shall be inserted;
2. the rows for the tariff quotas with order numbers 09.2975, 09.2603, 09.2935, 09.2814 and 09.2620 shall be replaced by the rows in Annex II to this Regulation.
